analysis.heading: Determining setbacks on oddly shaped lots considerations
analysis.content: Fig 17. Setbacks for oddly shaped lots
figures: A: Flag lot with front lot line closest and parallel to street
C: Substandard corner lot with frontage < 50'
E: Wedge shaped lot without rear lot lines
F: Lot with more than 4 sides
G: Lot with more than 4 sides and interior side yard
codes: Street side setback is 10' instead of 16'
Wedge shaped lots rear yard determined by a 20' radius from intersection of side lot lines
Rear lot line is farthest and most parallel to street
